{"tid":59334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣外交部：正式認定蔡英文過境美國","createTime":"2016-12-29T14:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T17:26:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f9597f5b085a921e660b2d93ace49b28a7c9cf","tid":59334,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_large_600_338/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/cyw_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_large_600_338%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fcyw_1.jpg&h=9589a0ae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣總統蔡英文明年初出訪中南美來回旅程將在美國中轉停留。台灣外交部今天正式肯定美國中轉行程，但具體中轉停留城市將留待下個星期宣布。媒體相信，蔡英文是否在紐約中轉，目前仍是未知數，其中蔡英文是否與美國當選總統特朗普或特朗普班底接觸是關鍵。中國官方今天再次強調反對蔡英文過境美國。 <br />\n<br />\n據路透社今天發自台北消息，台灣外交部證實蔡英文不久將成行的中南美訪問，首站危地馬拉旅程，將在美國做停機中轉。 <br />\n<br />\n路透社說，此消息必將進一步激怒北京。中國大陸本月初就要求美國禁止蔡英文在美國做停機中轉，北京指控蔡英文謀求通過停機中轉尋求國際承認分裂與獨立。中國大陸強調台灣是中國一個省份，是不可分割領土。 <br />\n<br />\n據路透社說，中國大陸與台灣的關係緊張本月急劇升高，台灣總統蔡英文與美國當選總統特朗普的直接通話引發北京憤怒。特朗普被指責挑戰中國堅持的一個中國立場與原則。 <br />\n<br />\n有消息指，台灣外交部沒有談及蔡英文所訪問國家是否有倒向中國大陸的危險。 <br />\n<br />\n國際廣播電台 <br />\n小山．報道"},{"pid":"a99cc53be19d82a0290260c5d0ec99490fd872f1","tid":59334,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84870415ea438b6e8e5c92ec6ce39ede010a12a5","tid":59334,"uid":43597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"美國洗聽你支那講野？"},{"pid":"ac72499a4621d60258924714325192e3722105e5","tid":59334,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"馬總統看錶"},{"pid":"5bb405c96b94203889fb56e7e33e9f4c7aa29c6f","tid":59334,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYEi9yq147FGAAuFAqt9JK3C6VK6DibH1PvBFLCHEDyd?filename=Lc87T3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc87T3.jpg&h=2f3a4a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUzmSQ2oH7XpGsatDWB345kjRipM5iEeZQ4k9oz8qEDWq?filename=hfLNg3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfLNg3.gif&h=fe97ee81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acb9135c3da08494f0e21353867a875832473fbc","tid":59334,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYEi9yq147FGAAuFAqt9JK3C6VK6DibH1PvBFLCHEDyd?filename=Lc87T3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc87T3.jpg&h=2f3a4a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPAhdLGe8BGJbQJb2WnJpRAjariHNwxY7w6FiYV1yKeUu?filename=hfLNg3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfLNg3.gif&h=fe97ee81&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec91bc7b785fed138b94a2321b424e571c44412b","tid":59334,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"侵：我比邊個過境關你支那撚事？"}]}